                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">With tactics, try charming a Sentry or Guardian Diaku up top, hasting and arming it with one weapon (they come equipped with one already, handy!) and having it take out two or three other diaku. Then, when your pet is low, you can 
<br />

<br />
1) break charm and charm another mob to kill it, if you have plenty of sentries and guardians around.
<br />

<br />
2) gate and come back in and recharm (cheesy but very effective)
<br />

<br />
3) have your pet sit down and wait until it regens (I have never done this hehe)
<br />

<br />
4) break charm and blur your pet until it regens. (cheesy, but since it was a nerf to us in the first place making them regen, I find it smehow fitting)
<br />

<br />
I find that if I get a good rhythm going, I can clear all the diaku from the area above the pit.</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
                        </tr>
                </table></td>
